reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Taller than anticipated, but cute and useful
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I used the measurements listed to ensure that these bins would fit into all the drawers.I must’ve miscalculated (or the measurements listed are slightly off) because they didn’t fit into the top 2 drawers on my changing table.That being said, I have gotten use out of them regardless!I’d recommend, just don’t expect them to fit into narrow drawers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for organizing 10"x11" storage cubes!
reviews.reviewText: I've been searching for "drawer organizers" that would work with those fabric storage cubes that measure 10"x11" - most organizers are for full sized dresser drawers. Not only do these fit perfectly, you can stack 2 layers of them in one storage cube! This has been perfect for organizing things where I've got stuff I need to access all the time (top layer) and related, but less frequently used items (bottom layer.) Love these so much I just ordered another set to layer up the rest of my storage cubes - it's like doubling their utility. Amazing!
